{"tid":2231684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歷史博物館「香港故事」關閉更新 獲邀作家爆館方研展覽提「中港邊境融合」","createTime":"2020-10-05T23:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T04:23:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e0319443d9ce9f1593805dfd248191115ae9148a","tid":2231684,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:45:58.000Z","msg":"香港歷史博物館早前宣佈，設展逾20年的常設展覽「香港故事」將於本月19日關閉以作更新，預計於2022年重開。歷史書作者余震宇日前透露，曾獲館方邀請提供有關香港海岸線變遷作展覽內容，但同時被要求進行有關「中港邊境融合」的歷史研究。余又指，館方同時提及新展覽包含開發郊野公園及人工島等尚未落實的計劃。康文署否認有關事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201006/URXIU2HUTZDOLH3FO6YQFPPCY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201006%2FURXIU2HUTZDOLH3FO6YQFPPCY4%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=dd9aa948\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201006%2FURXIU2HUTZDOLH3FO6YQFPPCY4%2F&h=247fa662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201006/URXIU2HUTZDOLH3FO6YQFPPCY4/</a>"},{"pid":"a2868fa4a1644231a89a3f721000c9fe05230209","tid":2231684,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83656975b40e0dadab4782711c3c0a7111d6d4a7","tid":2231684,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2c6cd20bda54678a32652072cdb13d7db7d2f7","tid":2231684,"uid":228955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:20:32.000Z","msg":"又搶拆